name: Find That File
tag_list: search, ftp, usenet, educational, file-search, document-search, video-search, audio-search
overview:
Find That File is a search engine used for locating downloadable media files such as documents, audio, video, compressed etc from the Web, FTP sites, Usenet and others.

The benefit of using Find That File is its ability to take a search term like “web” style engines and search for all types of possible files the user may want in classic facets, providing an extremely diverse and customizable experience.

In addition vertical subsets include : http://www.findthatdoc.com - Search Word and other Document Files http://www.findthatexcel.com - Search Excel Spreadsheets and other Spreadsheet Documents http://www.findthatpdf.com - Search PDF/Adobe Acrobat related Files http://www.findthatdll.com - Search Windows DLL and OCX System Components http://www.findthatzipfile.com - Search ZIP and more Compressed Archives http://www.findthatpowerpoint.com - Search PowerPoint Presentations, Slide Shows and Documents http://www.findthatrpm.com - Search Linux RPM Installer Packages http://www.findthatjar.com - Search JAVA JAR Files and Classes http://www.findthatcode.com - Search Source Code Files from Various Langauges http://www.findthatdb.com - Search Database Files http://www.findthatexe.com - Search Executables Files, Mac Installers and other Executables http://www.findthataudio.com - Search Audio Files http://www.findthatvideo.com - Search Video Files
